<font color="#FF0000">THEY ARE BITING, BUT NOT ME</font><br>
<tt>Sun Sep 14  0:57:45 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
A 100 things scream in me head wanting to be released and posted. But, I will stay on my side of the lake, and calmly fish. Thank you Cook, for keeping your word, and not dragging me into this latest round.  Someday we can try and pick it up again, but as for now, the keyboard is at home, so is the laptop, the cooler is filled with cold ones, the fish are biting, and I got my feet up. Life is good on Lake Peaceful Understanding. You guys can debate the great issues, I will keep on floating out here, on my side, and guess what, I might just buy a boat one of these days &lt;g&gt;<br><br>
doc spatz
